Discworld ritual help
crippling fatigue

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Crippling fatigue -- strikes down your enemies with debilitating weakness
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Crippling fatigue allows you to weaken an enemy, with the assistance of your deity of choice, for a limited duration of time.  It requires a holy symbol and will consume a block of incense.
.EP
